history.content:
Does anyone have any experience having the registrar's office change the dept name on their transcripts for cross-enrollment courses.

I took Chem C191, which is the cross enrollment course for CS C191, quantum computing. I ended up doing pretty well in the course, and I'm worried grad schools aren't going to recognize that it was within my major when reviewing my transcript. Ideally, since I could have it modified to say CS191.
